移除青少年模式弹窗 = type=http-response, pattern=^https:\/\/acs\.youku\.com\/gw\/mtop\.youku\.huluwa\.dispatcher\.youthmode\.config2, script-path=https://kelee.one/Resource/Script/YouKu_Video/YouKu_Video_remove_ads.js, requires-body=true, script-update-interval=0

